  "text": "The L-9 Azoarcus ribozyme (195 nt) was prepared by run-off transcription of pAz-IVS DNA digested with EarI and purified by PAGE as previously described by [CITATION_1] and . Purified RNA was resuspended in TE (10 mM Tris-HCl [pH 7.5], 0.1 mM EDTA) or CE (10 mM sodium cacodylate [pH 7.5], 0.1 mM EDTA) and incubated 5 min at 50 C before use.",
